						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment made by <hi rend="bold">Maḻapāḍaṉ Maḻapāḍi</hi> a merchant of <hi rend="bold">Nandipuram</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Āyirattaḷi</hi>, for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tiruchchōṟṟuttuṟai-Mādēva with an <hi rend="italic">uḻakku</hi> of ghee every day, and the setting up of an image of the goddess as consort of [Vēdi]-Viḍaṅgar (procession image), by the same donor.</p>						

						</summary>
